data.description: WELCOME HOME to this 3 bed/2 bath brick ranch w/ a basement in Brownsburg on an almost 1/2 acre wooded lot. Seller offering Special Financing. Enter the front door and be greeted by heaps of natural light. Updates galore-alongside original hardwood/tile flooring. Convenient & ample storage throughout. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet. Spacious primary bath. Formal dining room. Eat-in kitchen. Finished basement with fireplace. Stunning sunroom. Peaceful large back deck. Fully fenced backyard. Great neighbors. Native, low maintenance landscaping. Close to parks/biking & walking trails/restaurants & highways. *updates listed in agent notes
